## 2. Available Skills

### 2.1 `<skill_legal_audit>` — Compliance Verification

**Purpose:** Audit any feature, document, or email for legal compliance (EU Directive 2023/970, RODO, EU AI Act, Kodeks Pracy).

**Invocation:**
```xml
