- ✅ Git-based deploy (push to main → auto-deploy)
- ✅ SSL via Let's Encrypt (automatic)
- ✅ Can manage multiple services (Next.js + FastAPI + Redis + Weaviate on same VPS)
- ❌ Manual Docker Compose = too much overhead for solo founder

